cast.overview: Phillip is a wealthy quadriplegic who needs a caretaker to help him with his day-to-day routine in his New York penthouse. He decides to hire Dell, a struggling parolee who's trying to reconnect with his ex and his young son. Despite coming from two different worlds, an unlikely friendship starts to blossom.
cast.title: The Upside

details.biography: A Philadelphia native, Julie Stackhouse has been acting on film and stage since the age of 10. She studies acting at Playhouse West-Philadelphia under the instruction of Tony Savant. Julie has also trained at Arthur Murray Dance Studios, providing her with the knowledge and skills to perform ballroom, Latin, and modern dance.
details.name: Julie Stackhouse
